7 AS INTRODUCED
8 An Act relating to revenue and taxation; amending 68
O.S. 2021, Section 1353, as last amended by Section
9 4, Chapter 441, O.S.L. 2024 (68 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 1353), which relates to apportionment of
10 revenues; modifying total amounts for Oklahoma
Tourism and Recreation; amending 68 O.S. 2021,
11 Section 50011, which relates to revenue and taxation
definitions; expanding the definition of tourism
12 promotion; providing an effective date; and declaring
an emergency.
13
14
